# Project 2: Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

## Objective
The goal of this project was to analyze the cleaned sales dataset to identify patterns, trends, distributions, and key business insights.

## Tools Used
- Excel

## Analysis Performed
- Calculated descriptive statistics:
  - Count
  - Mean
  - Median
  - Minimum
  - Maximum
- Created Pivot Tables to summarize the data.
- Developed charts to visualize sales trends and distributions.
- Identified trends and potential outliers.
- Documented key observations from the analysis.

## Outcome
The analysis provided valuable insights into sales performance, customer behavior, and product trends.

## Files Included
- EDA Workbook
- Pivot Tables
- Charts
- Summary Report
